    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This specimen is mechanically flawless, having undergone preventative rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers precise gate engagement, paired with a limited-slip variable M differential. The factory paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the suspension retains its original kinematics with fresh bushings and dampers. A true collector-grade example with a documented service history and climate-controlled storage pedigree.",
